    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# üì© Workflow 5: Send Feedback Form after Invoice Paid  \n\n## üöÄ Process  \n1. **Webhook Node**  \n   - In Airtable, once the **Invoice Status = Paid**, the **Send Feedback** button becomes active.  \n   - When pressed, Airtable triggers a **Webhook** in n8n. \n   - Webhook Captures client details from Airtable (Name, Email, Project ID).  \n\n2. **Send Feedback Email (Gmail Node)**  \n   - Subject: ‚ÄúWe‚Äôd love your feedback on [Project Name]‚Äù  \n   - Body: Includes a link to the **Typeform feedback survey**.  \n   - Sent directly to the client‚Äôs email.  \n\n# üìù Workflow 6: Process Feedback Submission via Typeform  \n\n\n## üöÄ Process  \n1. **Typeform Trigger Node**  \n    - A client submits the **Typeform feedback survey**.  \n    - The **Typeform Trigger Node** activates in n8n.  \n    - Captures feedback responses along with the client‚Äôs email.  \n\n2. **Airtable Lookup**  \n   - Find the corresponding record in Airtable using the client‚Äôs email.  \n\n3. **Update Airtable Record**  \n   - Save the feedback answers into the record.  \n   - Update project status:  \n     - `Project Status = Closed`  \n     - `Feedback = [Responses from Typeform]`  \n\n\n",
